Adds a few facts about the disk drives in your systems
currently it supports Xen domU drives, IDE and SCSI/SATA
disks.

Xen domU:

    diskdrives => xvda
    diskmodel_xvda => Xen Virtual Disk
    disksize_xvda => 20971520
    disktype_xvda => xvd

Physical Server - SATA:
   
    diskdrives => sda,sdb
    diskmodel_sda => SAMSUNG HD403LJ 
    diskmodel_sdb => SAMSUNG HD403LJ 
    disksize_sda => 781422768
    disksize_sdb => 781422768
    disktype_sda => scsi
    disktype_sdb => scsi

